<item>
            <title>[LU-11471] IO Errors during failover  with very few number of OSTs</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-11471</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;one of our customer is noticed IO errors during failover with fewer OST.  we would like to add a  note into the Best practice section or OST planning section &lt;br/&gt;
========================&lt;br/&gt;
During  Fail over situation with few OSTs possibly cause I/O errors on the client side. &lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment>Lustre 2.5.X &lt;br/&gt;
</environment>
        <key id="33847">LU-11471</key>
            <summary>IO Errors during failover  with very few number of OSTs</summary>
                <type id="1" iconUrl="https://jira.whamcloud.com/secure/viewavatar?size=xsmall&amp;avatarId=11303&amp;avatarType=issuetype">Bug</type>
